From 0a8e32f9feafe8c3d435ffce44e3f6bc96704ef1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Sun, 7 Jun 2026 18:05:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Fix production readiness issues for RhythmicSpace v1.0

- Fix session recall: preset browser no longer overwrites restored state on open
- Apply full preset parameters (knobs + steps) when loading presets
- Fix filter type parameter read and wire filter combo to APVTS
- Remove duplicate reverb dry/wet mixing
- Add sample-accurate sequencer stepping with sub-block processing
- Add thread-safe step data access and MIDI map locking
- Persist MIDI mappings and transport sync state in plugin state
- Sync transport atomics from APVTS on session restore
- Implement pan rate LFO, stereo filter channels, and tail length reporting
- Fix user preset save/delete and disable JUCE splash screen
